# EAS Ignore
# Aggressively reduce upload size by ignoring all non-source artifacts

# --- NATIVE BUILD ARTIFACTS ---
# Ignore ALL build and temporary folders in android/ios
**/android/build/
**/android/app/build/
**/android/.gradle/
**/android/.cxx/
**/android/app/.cxx/
**/android/app/.externalNativeBuild/
**/ios/build/
**/ios/Pods/
**/ios/DerivedData/
**/ios/.xcode.env.local

# --- EXPO / METRO / CACHE ---
**/.expo/
**/dist/
**/web-build/
**/node_modules/
.metro-health-check*

# --- LOGS AND TEMP FILES ---
*.txt
*.log
*.sql
*.sqlite
npm-debug.*
yarn-debug.*
yarn-error.*

# --- IDE / OS FILES ---
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
